"{\"uid\": \"newsweek.com-high-speed-rail-eurostar-closure-delay-vacationers-paris-olympics-1922280\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Published  Jul 09, 2024 at 05:35 AM EDT  News Reporter  Vacationers planning to travel by train between Belgium, France, and the U.K. in the second half of August are set to face delays.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 186, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 104, \"end\": 111, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belgium\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.1618705042099763e-18, \"text\": \"Belgium\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belgium\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belgium\"}, {\"begin\": 113, \"end\": 119, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9998425180958095, \"rank\": 0.00012334747667722192, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}, {\"begin\": 129, \"end\": 133, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9942996414112207, \"rank\": 0.0057330388833270055, \"text\": \"U.K.\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Eurostar, a high-speed rail line between Belgium and the French border will be shut down for engineering works, extending journey times by about half an hour.\", \"from\": 188, \"to\": 350, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 192, \"end\": 200, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eurostar\", \"score\": 0.9999999994117843, \"rank\": 5.88133571844878e-10, \"text\": \"Eurostar\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eurostar\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eurostar\"}, {\"begin\": 233, \"end\": 240, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belgium\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.1618705042099763e-18, \"text\": \"Belgium\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belgium\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belgium\"}, {\"begin\": 249, \"end\": 255, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9088992856295766, \"rank\": 0.09986392096374547, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This closure, announced by Belgium's train operator SNCB, rail network infrastructure operator Infrabel, and Eurostar, aims to address signs of aging in the rail infrastructure.\", \"from\": 352, \"to\": 529, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 379, \"end\": 386, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belgium\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.1618705042099763e-18, \"text\": \"Belgium\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belgium\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belgium\"}, {\"begin\": 447, \"end\": 455, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Infrabel\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Infrabel\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Infrabel\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Infrabel\"}, {\"begin\": 461, \"end\": 469, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eurostar\", \"score\": 0.9999999994117843, \"rank\": 5.88133571844878e-10, \"text\": \"Eurostar\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eurostar\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eurostar\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Infrabel has identified aging issues in thehigh-speedline connecting Brussels to the French-Belgian border.\", \"from\": 531, \"to\": 638, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 531, \"end\": 539, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Infrabel\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Infrabel\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Infrabel\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Infrabel\"}, {\"begin\": 600, \"end\": 608, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brussels-South_railway_station\", \"score\": 0.999999916700748, \"rank\": 8.329873127133798e-08, \"text\": \"Brussels\", \"types\": [\"Q719456\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brussels-South_railway_station\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brussels-South_railway_station\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This section, the oldest on Belgium's high-speed network, is now 27 years old.\", \"from\": 640, \"to\": 718, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 668, \"end\": 675, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belgium\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.1618705042099763e-18, \"text\": \"Belgium\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belgium\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belgium\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"To tackle these issues, Infrabel has planned a decade-long renewal project.\", \"from\": 719, \"to\": 794, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 743, \"end\": 751, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Infrabel\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Infrabel\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Infrabel\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Infrabel\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"While most of the work will be done at night, a two-week full closure of the line each summer will be necessary.\", \"from\": 796, \"to\": 908, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The engineering works will begin on August 12, immediately following the closing ceremony of the ParisOlympics, which will take place on August 11.\", \"from\": 910, \"to\": 1057, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Over 18 days and nights, technical teams will overhaul one of the two tracks on a 17.6 kilometer stretch between the Belgian towns of Leuze-en-Hainaut and Brugelette.\", \"from\": 1059, \"to\": 1225, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1176, \"end\": 1183, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belgium\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.0399008934632842e-15, \"text\": \"Belgian\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belgium\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belgium\"}, {\"begin\": 1193, \"end\": 1209, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leuze-en-Hainaut\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Leuze-en-Hainaut\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leuze-en-Hainaut\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leuze-en-Hainaut\"}, {\"begin\": 1214, \"end\": 1224, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brugelette\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Brugelette\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brugelette\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brugelette\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This involves laying 35.2 km of new rails, 30,000 new sleepers, and 5,500 tons of ballast.\", \"from\": 1226, \"to\": 1316, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"During this period, Eurostar trains between Brussels and destinations such as Lille, Amsterdam, and Cologne will be diverted onto classic lines, adding approximately 30 minutes to travel times.\", \"from\": 1318, \"to\": 1511, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1338, \"end\": 1346, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eurostar\", \"score\": 0.9999999994117843, \"rank\": 5.88133571844878e-10, \"text\": \"Eurostar\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eurostar\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eurostar\"}, {\"begin\": 1362, \"end\": 1370, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brussels-South_railway_station\", \"score\": 0.999999916700748, \"rank\": 8.329873127133798e-08, \"text\": \"Brussels\", \"types\": [\"Q719456\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brussels-South_railway_station\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brussels-South_railway_station\"}, {\"begin\": 1396, \"end\": 1401, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lille-Flandres_station\", \"score\": 0.9999980992829351, \"rank\": 1.518647395206756e-06, \"text\": \"Lille\", \"types\": [\"Q719456\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lille-Flandres_station\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lille-Flandres_station\"}, {\"begin\": 1403, \"end\": 1412, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amsterdam_Centraal_station\", \"score\": 0.999999999808324, \"rank\": 1.916527304780847e-10, \"text\": \"Amsterdam\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amsterdam_Centraal_station\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amsterdam_Centraal_station\"}, {\"begin\": 1418, \"end\": 1425, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cologne\", \"score\": 0.9999999999988631, \"rank\": 4.4821872653587387e-13, \"text\": \"Cologne\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cologne\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cologne\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"SNCB trains will also be adjusted, affecting national journeys between Brussels, Mons, Ath, and Mouscron.\", \"from\": 1513, \"to\": 1618, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1584, \"end\": 1592, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brussels-South_railway_station\", \"score\": 0.999999916700748, \"rank\": 8.329873127133798e-08, \"text\": \"Brussels\", \"types\": [\"Q719456\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brussels-South_railway_station\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brussels-South_railway_station\"}, {\"begin\": 1609, \"end\": 1617, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mouscron\", \"score\": 0.9997329873321993, \"rank\": 0.0002670805575691508, \"text\": \"Mouscron\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mouscron\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mouscron\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Additionally, from August 12 to October 25, Austrian rail operator \\u00d6BB will suspend its Nightjet service between Brussels and Berlin due to ongoing works in France and Germany.\", \"from\": 1620, \"to\": 1796, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1664, \"end\": 1672, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Austria\", \"score\": 0.999801233556296, \"rank\": 7.666008621033642e-05, \"text\": \"Austrian\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Austria\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Austria\"}, {\"begin\": 1687, \"end\": 1690, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Deutsche_Bahn\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.4041124692357266e-41, \"text\": \"\\u00d6BB\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Deutsche_Bahn\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Deutsche_Bahn\"}, {\"begin\": 1733, \"end\": 1741, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brussels-South_railway_station\", \"score\": 0.999999916700748, \"rank\": 8.329873127133798e-08, \"text\": \"Brussels\", \"types\": [\"Q719456\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brussels-South_railway_station\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brussels-South_railway_station\"}, {\"begin\": 1746, \"end\": 1752, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Berlin_Hauptbahnhof\", \"score\": 0.9999999977721927, \"rank\": 2.227653598294261e-09, \"text\": \"Berlin\", \"types\": [\"Q719456\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Berlin_Hauptbahnhof\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Berlin_Hauptbahnhof\"}, {\"begin\": 1777, \"end\": 1783, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9998425180958095, \"rank\": 0.00012334747667722192, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}, {\"begin\": 1788, \"end\": 1795, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Germany\", \"score\": 0.9941874255553044, \"rank\": 0.0057982241086230015, \"text\": \"Germany\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Germany\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Germany\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The European Sleeper night trains will continue to operate between Brussels and Berlin, extending to Prague via Amsterdam.\", \"from\": 1797, \"to\": 1919, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1864, \"end\": 1872, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brussels-South_railway_station\", \"score\": 0.999999916700748, \"rank\": 8.329873127133798e-08, \"text\": \"Brussels\", \"types\": [\"Q719456\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brussels-South_railway_station\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brussels-South_railway_station\"}, {\"begin\": 1877, \"end\": 1883, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Berlin_Hauptbahnhof\", \"score\": 0.9999999977721927, \"rank\": 2.227653598294261e-09, \"text\": \"Berlin\", \"types\": [\"Q719456\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Berlin_Hauptbahnhof\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Berlin_Hauptbahnhof\"}, {\"begin\": 1898, \"end\": 1904, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Prague\", \"score\": 0.9999999707924876, \"rank\": 1.8495225289668394e-08, \"text\": \"Prague\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Prague\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Prague\"}, {\"begin\": 1909, \"end\": 1918, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amsterdam_Centraal_station\", \"score\": 0.999999999808324, \"rank\": 1.916527304780847e-10, \"text\": \"Amsterdam\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amsterdam_Centraal_station\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amsterdam_Centraal_station\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Travelers should prepare for longer journey times and potential schedule changes during the high-speed rail closure.\", \"from\": 1921, \"to\": 2037, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"SNCB, Infrabel, and Eurostar are coordinating to minimize disruption, but passengers are advised to check updated schedules and plan accordingly.\", \"from\": 2039, \"to\": 2184, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2045, \"end\": 2053, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Infrabel\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Infrabel\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Infrabel\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Infrabel\"}, {\"begin\": 2059, \"end\": 2067, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eurostar\", \"score\": 0.9999999994117843, \"rank\": 5.88133571844878e-10, \"text\": \"Eurostar\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eurostar\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eurostar\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As the renewal project continues over the next decade, annual summer closures can be expected, each involving extensive maintenance and upgrades.\", \"from\": 2186, \"to\": 2331, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The current phase is crucial to ensuring the long-term safety and reliability of thehigh-speed railnetwork, with future works likely to follow a similar pattern.\", \"from\": 2333, \"to\": 2494, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In the interim, passengers traveling between Belgium, France, and the U.K. should anticipate delays and consider alternative routes or travel methods if necessary.\", \"from\": 2496, \"to\": 2659, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2541, \"end\": 2548, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belgium\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.1618705042099763e-18, \"text\": \"Belgium\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belgium\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belgium\"}, {\"begin\": 2550, \"end\": 2556, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9998425180958095, \"rank\": 0.00012334747667722192, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}, {\"begin\": 2566, \"end\": 2570, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9942996414112207, \"rank\": 0.0057330388833270055, \"text\": \"U.K.\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Do you have a story we should be covering?\", \"from\": 2661, \"to\": 2703, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Do you have any questions about high-speed rail?\", \"from\": 2704, \"to\": 2752, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"ContactLiveNews@newsweek.com  \\u00a92025Newsweek Digital LLC\", \"from\": 2753, \"to\": 2808, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2769, \"end\": 2781, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Newsweek\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"newsweek.com\", \"types\": [\"Q41298\", \"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Newsweek\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Newsweek\"}]}]}"